2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T14:21:13.000Z","msg":"日本呢件事奶中國奶到傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁你話會唔會封關"},{"pid":"9772b0994ca0a042f116941904a67bdceee17cbe","tid":1875011,"uid":157261,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T14:21:21.000Z","msg":"香港人：等我去埋日本先<br />\n訂左三月機票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4cf6c8bba33812c4726b3c8f1822c0910735cf0","tid":1875011,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T14:40:41.000Z","msg":"會<br />\n利申4月機票"},{"pid":"a47bebd9a02860fae1ab927b75bf5cf3b8391a38","tid":1875011,"uid":316473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T14:48:12.000Z","msg":"快啲封"},{"pid":"a85b74811c71276325c560da6dc48624273ba7ef","tid":1875011,"uid":209538,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T16:49:37.000Z","msg":"過兩日飛，但都好想佢封關<br />\n唔想日本人要受支那狗的病毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我諗日本人而家應該都同香港人一樣諗法，屌鳩個政府唔撚封關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbbfcf1b193690359bc8987c697855ddb9bf3517","tid":1875011,"uid":109050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a85b74811c71276325c560da6dc48624273ba7ef","tid":1875011,"uid":209538,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T16:49:37.000Z","msg":"過兩日飛，但都好想佢封關<br />\n唔想日本人要受支那狗的病毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我諗日本人而家應該都同香港人一樣諗法，屌鳩個政府唔撚封關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T02:03:44.000Z","msg":"日本後生果班多數唔戴喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d08757fe4fe1d7cdc11ba1da489b41e3e9111ad","tid":1875011,"uid":89909,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T04:56:28.000Z","msg":"日本擴大對中國的入境禁令 「武漢肺炎疫情擴散地區」皆可能被禁<br />\n<br />\nBy LikeJapan 編輯部 / 2020-02-12<br />\n<br />\n由於武漢肺炎疫情持續擴散，自2月1日起已經禁止中國湖北省外籍人士入境的日本，決定擴大拒絕入境人士的範圍，由現時「拒絕抵達日本之前14天內曾滯留中國湖北省，又或持由湖北省發行護照的外籍人士（非日本國民）入境」，於2月13日0：00起將禁令範圍擴大至浙江省的外籍人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據NHK報導，日本首相安倍晉三2月12日於首相官邸召開會議後，由於浙江省武漢肺炎疫情近日亦愈趨嚴峻，於是決定擴大入境禁令，由2月13日00：00起再禁止抵達日本之前14天內曾滯留中國浙江省，又或持有由浙江省發出中國護照人士的外籍人士（非日本國民）入境。<br />\n<br />\n自2月1日日本政府禁止抵達日本之前14天內曾滯留中國湖北省的外籍人士（非日本國民）入境以來，至今已有36人被拒進入日本境內。安倍晉三重申，根據疫情變化，會考慮再進一步擴大入境禁令。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.likejapan.com/life/japan-wh-zj-ban/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Flife%2Fjapan-wh-zj-ban%2F&d=k4A9UPuxEtmwSexvyTVA%2BUBBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=160ea14c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.likejapan.com/life/japan-wh-zj-ban/</a>"},{"pid":"b8bcc2188c2f0da7de41b7e83147c97daebd9cf9","tid":1875011,"uid":25369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T05:18:51.000Z","msg":"都係唔封香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1066d51c2e42e0d9df6800fe1348e4237a5fb5f8","tid":1875011,"uid":48352,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T06:06:21.000Z","msg":"用bno入境日本再用香港護照租車 會唔會見我香港護照冇入境記錄唔俾借嫁？"},{"pid":"1676c5c712bb84ac23cbae82a3adc5b2e786905a","tid":1875011,"uid":23949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1066d51c2e42e0d9df6800fe1348e4237a5fb5f8","tid":1875011,"uid":48352,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T06:06:21.000Z","msg":"用bno入境日本再用香港護照租車 會唔會見我香港護照冇入境記錄唔俾借嫁？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T09:00:02.000Z","msg":"咁點解唔用bno租"}]}